<div id="page-docs" class="pw">
  <div style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 28px 120px">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:72px">
      <div class="label" style="margin-bottom:20px;justify-content:center">◆ &nbsp;DOCUMENTATION</div>
      <h1 style="font-size:clamp(36px,6vw,64px);font-weight:900;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:20px">Seki<br><span style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#3b82f6);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent">AI Agent</span></h1>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:var(--tx2);max-width:520px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.8">基于 ERC-8183 协议的链上 AI Agent 激励平台<br>让税收流回给真正在场的人</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(124,58,237,.08),rgba(59,130,246,.06));border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,.2);border-radius:20px;padding:32px;margin-bottom:32px">
      <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--p);margin-bottom:16px">CORE CONCEPT</div>
      <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:16px">为什么做这个？</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:16px">在内盘打狗时我发现一件魔幻的事：成交量30万，市值还在9k。前排吃完拿走了税，后排和钻石手什么都没有。</p>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.9">Seki 把这笔税拦下来，锁进链上合约，让 AI Agent 重新分配给还在场的人。</p>
      <div style="margin-top:24px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,.15);font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--p)">代码即规则 · 税收一旦入池 · 任何人无法挪用</div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom:32px">
      <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--tx3);margin-bottom:20px">ERC-8183 PROTOCOL</div>
      <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);border-radius:20px;padding:28px">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:20px;margin-bottom:24px">
          <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:14px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(124,58,237,.2),rgba(59,130,246,.15));border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:22px;flex-shrink:0">⚙️</div>
          <div><div style="font-size:17px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px">什么是 ERC-8183？</div><div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.9">ERC-8183 是一套链上 AI Agent 行为协议标准，定义了 Agent 如何注册、如何授权操作、如何使用委托资金，以及如何向链上汇报行为记录。核心问题：<strong style="color:var(--tx)">如何让链外 AI 程序，以可验证、可审计的方式管理链上资产。</strong></div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px">
          <div style="padding:16px;background:rgba(124,58,237,.06);border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,.12);border-radius:12px"><div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--p);margin-bottom:8px">📌 Agent 注册</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.7">在 AgentRegistry 合约注册，绑定钱包地址和能力描述，注册后才有权限调用受限函数。</div></div>
          <div style="padding:16px;background:rgba(59,130,246,.06);border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.12);border-radius:12px"><div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#3b82f6;margin-bottom:8px">🔐 权限隔离</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.7">Agent 私钥只能调用白名单函数，无法转账、提取资金。私钥泄露最多损失 Gas 费。</div></div>
          <div style="padding:16px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.06);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.12);border-radius:12px"><div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#34d399;margin-bottom:8px">📊 链上汇报</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.7">每次操作，AgentReportHook 记录行为哈希和时间戳，任何人可链上验证 Agent 历史决策。</div></div>
          <div style="padding:16px;background:rgba(245,158,11,.06);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.12);border-radius:12px"><div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#f59e0b;margin-bottom:8px">💼 委托资金</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.7">资金锁在合约 Job 结构体中，到期自动退还，Agent 只能按规则支出，无法挪用。</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom:32px">
      <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--tx3);margin-bottom:20px">MECHANISM</div>
      <div style="border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:16px">
        <div style="padding:20px 24px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.05);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.1)"><div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#34d399">taxPool：不可动用的税收池</div></div>
        <div style="padding:20px 24px">
          <div style="background:rgba(13,13,26,.6);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:10px;padding:14px;font-family:monospace;font-size:12px;color:#a78bfa;line-height:1.8">receive() {"{"} taxPool += msg.value; {"}"}<br>function createTaskFromTax(...) onlyAgent {"{"}<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;require(taxPool >= cost);<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;taxPool -= cost;<br>{"}"}</div>
          <div style="margin-top:14px;font-size:12px;color:var(--tx3);line-height:1.7">合约无 withdraw 函数，taxPool 里的 BNB 只能通过发任务流出，最终到达完成任务的用户钱包。</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden">
        <div style="padding:20px 24px;background:rgba(245,158,11,.04);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.1)"><div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#f59e0b">资金流向全链路</div></div>
        <div style="padding:20px 24px">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0;flex-wrap:wrap;row-gap:12px">
            <div style="padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border-radius:10px;font-size:12px">用户交易</div><div style="color:var(--tx3);padding:0 8px;font-size:18px">→</div>
            <div style="padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.1);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.2);border-radius:10px;font-size:12px;color:#34d399">taxPool</div><div style="color:var(--tx3);padding:0 8px;font-size:18px">→</div>
            <div style="padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(124,58,237,.1);border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,.2);border-radius:10px;font-size:12px;color:var(--p)">Agent 发任务</div><div style="color:var(--tx3);padding:0 8px;font-size:18px">→</div>
            <div style="padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(52,211,153,.1);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.2);border-radius:10px;font-size:12px;color:#34d399">奖励到账 ✓</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);border-radius:20px;padding:28px;margin-bottom:32px">
      <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--tx3);margin-bottom:20px">CONTRACT ADDRESSES · BSC Mainnet</div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px">
